# =============================================================================
# Zoro-Zero: Version Control Exclusions (.gitignore)
# Licensed under the MIT License (https://opensource.org/license/mit)
# Team-404, Michelle Stonecastle-20260527: v1.0.0
#
# DESCRIPTION:
#   Shields sensitive credentials (.env), heavy multi-gigabyte models (.ollama/),
#   external vendor source packages (upstream-hermes-agent/), and standard
#   operating system and editor trash from being committed to GitHub.
# =============================================================================

# Local Upstream Source
upstream-hermes-agent/

# Local Environment & Secrets
.env

# Local Container State & Ollama Models
.ollama/

# IDEs & Editor Configuration Files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# Operating System Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# AI Agent Configs & Brain Caches
.gemini/

# Internal Documentation & Personal Runlogs
.docs/


